<div id="banner">
	<h1>EFF Rudeness</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Aahz: <a href="http://www.rahul.net/aahz/eff.html">Rudeness for rudeness, an open letter to the EFF</a>. &#8220;Had Brad behaved this way with almost anyone else, I would not feel compelled to write this letter &#8212; it would be self-evident that Brad was behaving badly. But precisely because it was Harlan Ellison who was the target, a man notorious for behaving badly, I feel the need to stand up and say that Brad&#8217;s behavior was wrong.&#8221;</p>

<p>See <a href="000292">our coverage of this event</a>.</p>

